✅BEARS!

I saw two grizzlies @yellowstonenps and one black bear @grandtetonnps. I spotted the bear in #LamarValley and they named me the “bear whisperer” 😂

A massive grizzly began to feed on a fallen bison. I’m told that I was lucky to catch that. A lady next me had a scope connected to her phone so we all sat for hours as the bear would feed then disappear into the creek to nap and play then come out to feed again. 

He was so territorial that he would pounce if the birds tried to sneak in a meal. I left while the others stayed for the 24 pack of wolves showed up. Your perspective changes when you realize that you are no longer at the top of the food chain. 😬

#Yellowstone #bucketlist #travel #montana #Wyoming #usa #bears
